        <Historic_Flag>Current</Historic_Flag>
        <Parent_String>target rifles [300218247], sporting firearms [300218246], sports and athletic equipment [300211035], recreational artifacts (equipment) [300218781], Recreational Artifacts (hierarchy name) [300136012], Furnishings and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300264551], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
        <Hier_Rel_Type>Genus/Species-BTG</Hier_Rel_Type>
